    <label>mechlord</label>
    <description>The Mechlord is the unnatural combination of a human and a Mechhive core. Their integrated persona core and mechlink subsystem gives them enhanced mental abilities and unmatched control over mechanoids. They also excel at building and working with technology. However, they are slow and sleepy, so they tend to rely on their mechanoids or their allies to do menial labor.</description>
    <descriptionShort>Mechlords excel at controlling mechanoids, and are good at building and working with technology. However, they are slow and sleepy, so they often rely on their mechanoids or allies.</descriptionShort>
